      "comment": "CALM LEGEND (1) faces the starter for the first time. By McWicked and hails from the Mat Rue stable. Has been showing ability at the trials and should enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. MUDDY MARVELLOUS (10) is a three-year-old gelding from the Nathan Turnbull yard on debut. Draws out a little on the second line and may need luck at some point but has not been far away in recent trials. Could kick off with a win. DETANGLED (9) has been thereabouts of late and is a chance to break through after a good effort from this row last time out when third at this circuit and distance. REDEMPTION MISS (8) cannot be left out after solid recent performances, beaten only 4.6m in a stronger race last start to follow a string of placings.",
